5.1 Vagrant support for VirtualBox,VMware, docker, Hyper-V
	vagrant init create a base machine i.e. ubuntu/bionic base image, which can be cloned to create other machine.
	
5.2 Box in vagrant means package format for Vagrant environments. In simple words, it is a virtual machine. 'A “box” is the base image used to create a virtual environment with Vagrant'
	vagrant box add ADDRESS 
	
